# These owners are reserved for exact retail-derived rebuild outputs
# materialized locally from a user-provided installation. Legitimate authored
# or separately provided assets belong in their normal source-owning path.
/rebuild/OnslaughtRebuild.Core/Assets/Level100/**
/rebuild/OnslaughtRebuild.Godot/Assets/Aquila/**
/rebuild/OnslaughtRebuild.Godot/Assets/Frontend/**
/rebuild/OnslaughtRebuild.Godot/Assets/Hud/**
